trans-unit.source: Defines a mechanism for retrieving a service contract from a component.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en metode for å hente en servicekontrakt fra en komponent.

trans-unit.source: The IServiceProviderContract interface defines a contract that enables a component to obtain a custom service that is defined by another component.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IServiceProviderContract definerer en kontrakt som gjør det mulig for en komponent for å hente en egendefinert tjeneste som er definert av en annen komponent.

trans-unit.source: A component that implements IServiceProviderContract is known as a service provider.
trans-unit.target: En komponent som implementerer IServiceProviderContract kalles en tjenesteleverandør.

trans-unit.source: Service providers implement the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract.QueryService%2A> method to return an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> that implements a service.
trans-unit.target: Tjenesteleverandører implementere den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract.QueryService%2A>metode til å returnere en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract>som implementerer en tjeneste.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract.QueryService%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns a service contract that is implemented by this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en servicekontrakt som implementeres av dette <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The formats of the strings that identify services and service contracts are defined by the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Formater av strenger som identifiserer tjenester og servicekontrakter er definert av den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>implementeringen.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>

trans-unit.source: It is recommended that <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract> implementations identify a service contract by the <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A> property of the type that implements the service contract.
trans-unit.target: Anbefales det at <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>implementeringer identifisere kontrakten av den <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A>egenskap av typen som implementerer servicekontrakten.</xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>

trans-unit.source: The name of the service that is being requested.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på tjenesten som blir sendt.

trans-unit.source: The service contract that is being requested.

An <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IContract"></xref> that represents a service contract that a client is requesting from the <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"></xref>; <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"></xref> does not implement the requested contract.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IContract"> </xref> som representerer en servicekontrakt som ber om en klient fra den <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"> </xref>; <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> hvis den <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"> </xref> implementerer ikke den forespurte kontrakten.
